The paper discusses the difficulties of learning logic programs, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper specifically focuses on the use of cut (!) in logic programming, which is a topic related to programming languages (cs.PL) and computational logic (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the need for intensional evaluation, which is a topic related to software engineering (cs.SE).
